### product search 재색인 - 기본 pageSize

POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/products/search/reindex
Accept: application/json

### product search 재색인 - pageSize 지정

POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/products/search/reindex?pageSize=1000
Accept: application/json

### product search 기본 조회 - averageRating 기본 정렬(desc)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=wire&size=20
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - averageRating 정렬(desc)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=wire&size=20&sort=averageRating&order=desc
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - averageRating cursor 기반 다음 페이지
### 아래 cursor 값은 이전 응답의 nextCursor로 교체해서 사용한다.

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=wire&size=20&sort=averageRating&order=desc&cursor=REPLACE_WITH_NEXT_CURSOR
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - ratingNumber 정렬(desc)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=wire&size=20&sort=ratingNumber&order=desc
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - price 정렬(asc)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=wire&size=20&sort=price&order=asc
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - price 정렬(desc)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=wire&size=20&sort=price&order=desc
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - 결과 없음

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=no-such-keyword&size=20
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - blank keyword

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=%20%20%20&size=20
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - keyword 누락(400)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?size=20
Accept: application/json

### product search 조회 - 잘못된 cursor(400)

GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?keyword=wire&size=20&sort=averageRating&order=desc&cursor=invalid-cursor
Accept: application/json
